@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<h1>Finance Tracker</h1>

<p>This application helps users build financial independence by tracking budgets, transactions, and savings goals.</p>

<ul>
    <li>Secure user authentication with ASP.NET Core Identity</li>
    <li>Budget categories and monthly limits</li>
    <li>Income and expense transaction tracking</li>
    <li>Savings goals with progress tracking</li>
    <li>Dashboard summary for monthly finances</li>
</ul>

<p>Use the navigation menu to open the feature modules.</p>
